Package: easyrdd
Type: Package
Title: Contains methods for implementing Regression Discontinuity Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2020-11-17
Author: person("Samuel", "Gailliot", email = "samuel.gailliot@stat.tamu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: <samuel.gailliot@stat.tamu.edu>
Description: The goal for this package is to perform estimation for single assignment RDD (both sharp and fuzzy) and implement optimal bandwidth selection using Imbens-Kalyanaraman method in an easy to use package.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
